column2: "How many times do I have to say it? It's this way! We've been past there twice already!"
"Shut up, it doesn't really matter. We're almost done, anyway."
"You're always like this! It's a matter of efficiency."
"But who was the one who messed up what we were supposed to be doing in the first place?"
"You always say that it doesn't matter, and then immediately go back on what you said! You suck!"
"Hey! Don't get on my case! You looked like you were going to cry back there."
"Don't talk about that. ...I did kind of screw up."
"Sorry, I wasn't trying to get on your case."
"We've been together since we were kids, so you know that right?"
"I know, I just don't want to be a burden."
"So... Echo, let's get back to the quest!"
"Right! The quest! We should probably get back to that!"
"You're right, but if somebody hadn't messed up, we'd already be done by now."
